```plantuml
@startuml jkahn117_aws-news
actor User
participant "Next.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "CloudFront CDN" as CloudFront
participant "AppSync GraphQL API" as AppSync
participant "Lambda Services" as Lambda
participant "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB
participant "ElastiCache Redis" as Redis
participant "S3 Storage" as S3
participant "EventBridge" as EventBridge
participant "Image Processor" as ImageProcessor
participant "Pinpoint Analytics" as Pinpoint
participant "Kinesis Firehose" as Firehose

User -> Frontend: Access AWS News
Frontend -> CloudFront: Request content
CloudFront -> AppSync: GraphQL query
AppSync -> Lambda: Resolve query
Lambda -> Redis: Check cache
alt Cache hit
    Redis --> Lambda: Return cached data
else Cache miss
    Lambda -> DynamoDB: Query metadata
    DynamoDB --> Lambda: Return metadata
    Lambda -> S3: Get article content
    S3 --> Lambda: Return content
    Lambda -> Redis: Cache results
end
Lambda --> AppSync: Return data
AppSync --> CloudFront: Return response
CloudFront --> Frontend: Display content

User -> Frontend: View article
Frontend -> Pinpoint: Track view event
Pinpoint -> Firehose: Stream analytics data

group Ingestion Process
    participant "RSS Fetcher" as RSSFetcher
    RSSFetcher -> Lambda: Trigger feed parsing
    Lambda -> DynamoDB: Store metadata
    Lambda -> S3: Store article content
    Lambda -> EventBridge: Publish article_created
    EventBridge -> ImageProcessor: Trigger processing
    ImageProcessor -> S3: Process/store images
    ImageProcessor -> DynamoDB: Update image references
end
@enduml
```